data.description: Nestled in the heart of North Portage, this ranch-style home is a delightful blend of modern updates and timeless comfort. From the stylish kitchen to the inviting living spaces, every detail reflects a commitment to quality living. The heart of this home is the kitchen featuring Hickory cabinets, laminate flooring, a glass tile backsplash, eat-up bar, pantry, eating area, and all appliances. A spacious living room adorned with cove ceilings, creating an inviting atmosphere. A separate entry welcomes guests and boasts a walk-in cedar coat closet, adding a touch of elegance. The home offers three bedrooms, each generously sized and featuring ample closet space. The backyard is completely fenced for your privacy. Two storage sheds provide practical solutions for your storage needs.
